A vintage 1950s-style illustration showing a cluttered junkyard of obsolete technology - towering piles of dusty CRT monitors, chunky beige computer towers, and tangled ethernet cables, all rendered in muted sepia and faded turquoise tones. In the foreground, a sleek modern laptop sits pristine on a small pedestal, glowing with warm golden light, creating stark contrast against the decaying tech graveyard behind it. The scene has the aesthetic of mid-century advertising artwork with halftone dot patterns and slightly worn paper texture, evoking nostalgia while clearly showing the passage of technological time. Dramatic shadows stretch across the junkyard as if cast by a setting sun, suggesting an era coming to an end.
